@startuml C4_Concern_Idempotency
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Cross-Cutting Concern - Idempotent Operations

Boundary(idempotency_model, "Idempotency Pattern") {
    Component(request, "Request", "Input", "User request")
    Component(idempotency_key, "IdempotencyKey", "UUID", "Request identifier")
    Component(deduplication, "DeduplicationCache", "Storage", "Request ↔ result mapping")
}

Boundary(request_handling, "Request Processing") {
    Component(cache_check, "CacheCheck", "Lookup", "Check dedup cache")
    Component(cache_hit, "CacheHit", "Found", "Return cached result")
    Component(cache_miss, "CacheMiss", "New", "Process request")
    Component(execute_task, "ExecuteTask", "Action", "Business logic")
    Component(cache_result, "CacheResult", "Store", "Save result")
}

Boundary(idempotent_ops, "Idempotent Operations") {
    Component(transfer_money, "TransferMoney", "Safe", "f(f(x)) = f(x)")
    Component(create_record, "CreateRecord", "Safe", "Duplicate create ignored")
    Component(update_status, "UpdateStatus", "Safe", "Idempotent update")
}

Boundary(non_idempotent, "Non-Idempotent Operations") {
    Component(increment, "Increment", "Unsafe", "f(f(x)) ≠ f(x)")
    Component(append, "Append", "Unsafe", "Duplicate append fails")
}

request --> idempotency_key: Generates
idempotency_key --> cache_check: Checks
cache_check --> cache_hit: If found
cache_check --> cache_miss: If new

cache_miss --> execute_task: Executes
execute_task --> cache_result: Saves
cache_result --> deduplication: Stores mapping
cache_hit --> request: Returns cached

idempotent_ops --> deduplication: Use pattern
non_idempotent --> deduplication: Avoid

Note as N1
Idempotency: f(f(x)) = f(x)
Calling same operation multiple times = calling once

Key Pattern:
1. Generate unique request ID (UUID)
2. Check deduplication cache
3. If hit → return cached result (fast!)
4. If miss → execute operation
5. Cache result with ID
6. Return result

Safe Operations (Idempotent):
✅ TransferMoney (idempotency key)
✅ CreateRecord (unique constraint)
✅ UpdateStatus (same value OK)

Unsafe Operations (Non-Idempotent):
❌ Increment counter
❌ Append to list
❌ Double-spend prevention

Requirements:
- Dedup cache size: ≥1000 entries
- TTL: ≥1 hour
- Collision probability: <0.001%
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
